-- Turkish May Tourists Rise 15.8 Percent, Gaining for 4th Month This Year
-- Ali Berat Meric
-- 2010-06-23T07:59:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/turkish-may-tourists-rise-15-8-percent-gaining-for-4th-month-this-year.html

          
          
             The number of foreign tourists
visiting Turkey rose 15.8 percent in May from a year earlier.  
 About 3.1 million foreign visitors arrived in the month, up
from 2.7 million in the same month of 2009, the Tourism Ministry
in Ankara said on its website today.  
